   COMMENTARY (``k'' category)
</P>
<P>
   JAPAN-RESILIENCY (Paris) _ Although things in Japan are rougher
than most people realized, don't count it out. The Japanese are a
highly resilient people. By BERNARD D. KAPLAN.
