and police informant, is acquitted of hiring his brother to kill
his estranged wife because she had filed for divorce and gone after
the millions he made in illegal gambling. Mrs. Angleton was shot
several times when she returned home to retrieve a softball bat. By
STEVE BREWER and STEFANIE ASIN.
