</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Spotlight on... Jeff Bridges
 &HT;    By Steve Murray
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``The Last Picture Show'': Living in small-town Texas in the
1950s in this acclaimed drama.
</P>
<P>
   ``Stay Hungry'': Pumping iron in the South, alongside an unknown
newcomer named Arnold Schwarzenegger.
</P>
<P>
   ``Starman'': Crash-landing on earth and romancing Karen Allen.
</P>
<P>
   ``Jagged Edge'': Lawyer Glenn Close wants to know whether he
killed his wife or it's a frame-up.
</P>
<P>
   ``The Morning After'': Another murder mystery, this time with
Jane Fonda as a boozing actress.
</P>
<P>
   ``The Fabulous Baker Boys'': Playing a lounge-act duo with
brother Beau and making beautiful music with vamp Michelle
Pfeiffer.
</P>
<P>
   ``Fearless'': Surviving a plane crash and looking at life in a
brand-new way.
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
