<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    LIVING THE DIPLOMATIC LIFE; ONE 'SOLITARY PACKAGE' AWAY FROM
VIOLENCE, INSECURITY
 &HT;    Moving in both the (i) International and (w) Washington
categories.
 &HT;    By Mark Sherman  
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service 
