<P>
   OBIT-ANDYGUMP (Los Angeles) _ Andy Gump, the king of California
portable toilets, died at 88 on Monday at his Southland home.
Gump's life, which took him from a Oklahoma childhood to industry
kingpin, reads like a Horatio Alger tale. By Dennis McCarthy. (Will
