<SLUG> BC-QUOTE-OF-THE-DAY-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-BBN-MCGWIRE-FANS-NYT, which
moved in ``s'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``I just wanted to make sure I got here and got a chance to get
something from his season. He's obviously going to break it. Even
if we don't get a ball, we can say we were here.''
</P>
<P>
   _CHAD MULLIGAN, one of thousands of Cardinals fans who show up
early to watch Mark McGwire take batting practice.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
